org.hibernate.search.cfg
Class FieldBridgeDirectMapping

java.lang.Object
  org.hibernate.search.cfg.PropertyMapping
      org.hibernate.search.cfg.FieldBridgeDirectMapping

public class FieldBridgeDirectMapping
extends PropertyMapping

As opposed to FieldBridgeMapping which is used as an option of Field, this mapping can be defined directly on the property. Mostly used when no Field is defined, such as on DocumentId.
